01:05:16.200 --> 01:05:18.880
the [INAUDIBLE] polarized
field as a superposition

01:05:18.880 --> 01:05:22.660
of left-handed and right-handed,
or counter-rotating

01:05:22.660 --> 01:05:25.370
and co-rotating magnetic field.

01:05:25.370 --> 01:05:26.550
So let me just do that.

01:05:32.920 --> 01:05:34.690
So we have the Z part.

01:05:39.980 --> 01:05:47.160
And now, instead of having
